{"tid":1359843,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"汪明荃指羅家英手術康復理想：佢小便自然","createTime":"2019-07-24T08:26:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T03:34:44.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"75fdf79d04a4650eedf66cbcab23c14b453b67d6","tid":1359843,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:26:15.000Z","msg":"汪明荃到電台宣傳9月底上演的多齣粵劇，阿姐透露已開始綵排，丈夫羅家英則剛由日本出席友人大壽返港，她說：「佢未開始排戲，要八月先開始排，佢今次做嘅戲唔係太複雜，我就要同新人演出，所以要排住先。」 <br />\n<br />\n講到早前剛接受完前列腺切除手術的羅家英健康情況，阿姐說：「OK呀，見佢小便嗰啲都好自然，日常生活都OK。（提佢注意飲食﹖）佢自己知，唔鍾意人提佢。（家英話你成日哦佢﹖）佢真係好夜瞓吖嘛，我都點幾瞓佢都未瞓，喺度睇電影。佢識照顧自己，大家唔使擔心，嚟緊仲有兩個廣告要拍，又要去返去橫掂拍嘢，佢呢排就真係發。（定期檢查傷口﹖）傷口冇事，因為佢割咗，依家等恢復番，半年後再檢查，好多男人到呢個年紀都有呢啲情況。」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190724/photo/bkn-20190724140154936-0724_00862_001_02p.jpg?20190724143138\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190724%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190724140154936-0724_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20190724143138&h=78be26d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190724/photo/bkn-20190724140154936-0724_00862_001_03p.jpg?20190724143138\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190724%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190724140154936-0724_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20190724143138&h=f99b43fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3087d86f49407558c2de7c1890092dab22e5a2bc","tid":1359843,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:11:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我</span></span>"},{"pid":"e8c72a6758a6c662391d213ec9367aac4eb4bf24","tid":1359843,"uid":227597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3087d86f49407558c2de7c1890092dab22e5a2bc","tid":1359843,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:11:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large